1
00:00:03,860 --> 00:00:08,780
All over the world, law enforcement is a key
aspect of protected area management.

2
00:00:08,780 --> 00:00:13,670
These territories are indeed filled with values
to protect.

3
00:00:13,670 --> 00:00:22,040
This protection is based on rules and regulations
defining what should be conserved and how.

4
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:29,200
Ethical, moral and professional principles
must be followed to implement these rules,

5
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:33,870
and strict methods must be used to give, assess
and execute orders.

6
00:00:33,870 --> 00:00:41,329
On the field, all this is reflected in best
practices leading to good results.

7
00:00:41,329 --> 00:00:46,470
This MOOC will cover all these topics over
5 modules that will help us:

8
00:00:46,470 --> 00:00:52,399
1- know the laws, conventions, rules applicable
… their rank, their scope and their limitations.

9
00:00:52,399 --> 00:00:56,640
2- discover the principles that go with
them, ethics in particular…

10
00:00:56,640 --> 00:01:01,460
3- conversely, assess the disastrous impact
of corruption…

11
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:06,439
4- and understand the importance of precision
when giving orders.

12
00:01:06,439 --> 00:01:15,880
5- Finally, illustrate how this is reflected
concretely in protected area surveillance.

13
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:22,630
We will present these modules with different
experts, namely lawyer, police officer, PA

14
00:01:22,630 --> 00:01:23,630
manager.

15
00:01:23,630 --> 00:01:29,740
Videos, quizzes, documents to read, a forum
to exchange, a Facebook group, online discussions. Everything

16
00:01:29,740 --> 00:01:34,619
is ready for you to progress at your own pace.

17
00:01:34,619 --> 00:01:37,760
There are no pre-requisites for registration.

18
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:44,100
And of course, you’ll have the possibility
to take the exams and receive a certificate

19
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:45,320
of completion.

20
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:50,650
There, join us now to explore this key aspect
of protected area management.

21
00:01:50,650 --> 00:01:51,969
See you very soon!

